\fs32 \cf0 \cb7 dev plan: Overview\
Integrate the story engine into V3's deterministic, frozen-plan architecture. In V3, stories are governed inserts proposed by the LLM but enforced by deterministic policy. Stories are selected by the LLM during plan generation and written into the plan YAML, subject to Story Slot Policy constraints. The Python assembler loads stories from the story bank and injects them into chapters, similar to how exercises are currently handled.\
\
