Validator Enforcement:\
\
Reject stories with story_role: "explanatory" (if detected)\
Reject stories longer than N words (configurable, default: 400 words per layer)\
Reject stories containing instruction language (e.g., "you should", "try this", "do this")\
Stories must be narrative, not didactic\
Story Role Definitions:\
\
Recognition (L1): Emotional mirror, problem recognition, "I see you"\
Effort (L2): First attempts, friction, movement toward change\
Return (L3): Integration, wisdom, healing arc\
Forbidden: Explanatory, instructional, prescriptive content\
